collections.name: Bar Fly Collection # 1
collections.description:
‘A Celebration of Cocktails Through an Abstract Lens’

Dive into the vibrant world of ‘Bar Fly’, a mesmerising NFT collection that transforms the essence of cocktails into stunning abstract art. Each piece in this collection is a visual toast to the creativity and craftsmanship behind your favorite drinks. From the classic elegance of a Martini to the tropical flair of a Piña Colada, ‘Bar Fly’ captures the spirit, colour, and emotion of cocktails like never before.

With every brushstroke, experience the swirling dance of flavors and aromas, reimagined through a kaleidoscope of colors and shapes. Let your senses be tantalized by the bold interpretations and playful compositions that bring each drink to life in a unique, abstract form.

Whether you're a cocktail connoisseur, an art enthusiast, or an NFT collector, ‘Bar Fly’ offers a one-of-a-kind blend of mixology and modern art. Immerse yourself in this intoxicating journey and own a piece of the cocktail experience.

collections.name: Horizons | by PixlGraph
collections.description:
Limited Edition 50 Pieces - Stored 100% on-chain for 100% ownership.

Nature stands as the quintessential generative artist, crafting masterpieces since the dawn of time. With every fleeting moment, nature unveils a new work of art-many destined to remain unseen. Horizons is a collaborative art project inspired by this concept: an endeavor to capture nature's ephemeral beauty and preserve it eternally on the blockchain. Each piece, derived from one of 50 original images, is algorithmically transformed into a compact array of 232 color blocks, optimized for efficient blockchain storage. These blocks are then chained together, forming an image that reveals nature's colorful artistry. Own a fragment of nature, forever frozen in time.

[NFT ART Buyers Benefits]
We will arrange special experiences in Japan, such as helicopter charter from Kansai Airport, limousine arrangement from Kyoto Station, reservations at luxury hotels and restaurants in Kyoto, and guided tours to the shooting locations, Mizushi Shrine and Inui Shrine.

Inui Shrine in Joyo, Kyoto, enshrines Oonui-no-Mikoto and Onui-no-Mikoto, who have long been worshipped as the "gods of sewing."
"縫" means to stitch cloth together with thread and needles, and to paint and sew clothes.
It's a true "holy land" for people in the apparel/fashion industry and cosplayers.

collections.description:
The Legless Leo Community Artist collection is an extension of the Legless Leo generative NFT collection that resides on ApeChain.  Legless Leo the character is based on Reaper's real life 3-legged dog (@Reaper_NFT).

This collection will grow over time with 1 of 1 art pieces from legendary artists in the digital art world, all representing Leo in their own unique style.

The primary focus of the Legless Leo project is to provide charitable donations to the Tripawds Foundation, a 501(3)c organization devoted to supporting pet amputees.  Our commitment is to make a charitable donation to Tripawds each month of at least 50% of the ongoing royalties.  Artwork from this collection will be rewarded to Legless Leo NFT holders who continue to support our cause.

collections.name: Eclat d'aquarelle
collections.description:
Éclats d'Aquarelle : Une histoire haute en couleurs 

Plongez dans un monde où chaque coup de pinceau raconte une histoire, où les couleurs dansent et s’entrelacent pour donner vie à des œuvres haute en couleurs. 

J'ai toujours été fasciné par la beauté et le rendu de l'aquarelle, je suis aujourd'hui devenu un artiste numérique qui à toujours chercher à obtenir cet aspect avec un logiciel de peinture, j'ai trouver mon style en mêlant l'aquarelle et la peinture traditionnelle.

"Éclats d'Aquarelle" est une collection unique d'œuvres numériques et élégante, inspiré des grands noms de l'aquarelle, fusionnée avec les technique de peinture numérique.
